  "description": "Tantalum, cobalt, and indium production for semiconductor-specific applications: TaN/Ta copper diffusion barriers (PVD and ALD sputtering targets), cobalt silicide (CoSi₂) self-aligned contacts, cobalt CMP slurries for contact planarization, ITO transparent conductors for displays, InGaAs photonic detectors, and indium bump bonding for flip-chip packaging. All three metals are on the GPU critical path.",
